           <p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">《管理思想》免费讲座</span></strong></span></p>
           <p style="text-align: center;"><strong style="color: rgb(192, 0, 0); font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">本微信每天播出1集讲座<br /></span></strong></p>
