              <p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="font-size: 20px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">《阿米巴+合伙人管理模式》</span></p>
