             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体; font-size: medium; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 22.7272720336914px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 16px; line-height: 22px; text-align: center; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">客户见证（部分列入）</span></p>
             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></p>
             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 19px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">金蝶软件公司（著名管理软件品牌），正大集团，红马传媒：大麦网 （20亿，行业第一名），成都正大集团 （30亿，饲料龙头企业），珠江钢管（40亿上市企业，行业第一名），宁波泰茂车业 （20亿），雅迪集团 （行业第一品牌），久泰能源 （30亿），盈聚电子（28亿），东鹏陶瓷 （50亿 知名品牌），金舵陶瓷 （25亿 知名品牌），中油中泰集团 （15亿），天耀集团 （10亿），博创集团 （8亿 行业标杆），天安新材股份 （7亿），科茂林化股份 （7亿 行业第一名），中烟摩迪 （8亿 行业第一名），北京仁达房地产评估 （行业第一名），中地地产评估（行业领头羊），广隆食品 （200多家连锁店），安能保险柜（行业第一品牌），锦绣明天（行业第一品牌），联合蓝海（行业第一品牌）....</span></p>
             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体; font-size: medium; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 22.7272720336914px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><img data-s="300,640" data-type="jpeg" data-ratio="1.37" data-w="400" width="auto" data-src="http://rdn.135editor.com/cache/remote/aHR0cHM6Ly9tbWJpei5xbG9nby5jbi9tbWJpei9tNzlZeHlraFIxdWhrYThWRnptbWpvRkdVMWt3UWFyQmZpYld6Z3FkeHVrY3lNMFNWaWFZUFBhdkZjMjV2bDdDQTJuYVU2ampDU2ljRVBmcGliTGhxdFVmZ0EvMD93eGZtdD1qcGVnJmFtcDt3eF9mbXQ9anBlZw==" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); line-height: 23.99147605896px; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: auto !important; visibility: visible !important;" class="lazy" /></p>
             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 宋体; font-size: medium; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 22.7272720336914px; text-align: center; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">【地点】：</span></strong></span><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 28px;">广州 鸿源酒店</span><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">【时间】：</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">8月29-30日（周六、周日、二天一夜）</span></span></p>
             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">【对象】：</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">董事长、总经理带领核心高管团队参课</span></span></span></p>
             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">【举办】：</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></strong><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">广州思想力文化传播有限责任公司，</span></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 28px;">官网：www.sxlwh.com </span></span></p>
             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">【费用】：</span></strong></span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">干货解决方案，物超所值</span></strong></span></span></p>
             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></strong></span></p>
             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">第20期课程内容继续升级，精益求精，实操干货！</span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></strong><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: red; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"></span></strong></span></p>
             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">1<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">、市场价7800元/人。<strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">即可学习系统解决方案干货，回去即可做适合自己企业的解决方案，节省昂贵的管理咨询费！本课程内容全部是管理咨询实战干货内容，不讲理论概念，不吹牛，不包装，不卖产品！</span></strong></span></span></p>
             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></p>
             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">2、</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; line-height: 28px;">企业团队价19800元（5人参课），前5家企业团队报名汇款可赠送一个免费名额，</span><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(192, 0, 0);"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">物超所值。本课程适合公司创始人与核心高管团队一起学习研讨解决方案（合伙人制度、核心团队建设、5R运营管理、OKR考核、文化建设等模块）！</span></strong></span></span></p>
             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(62, 62, 62); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: medium; line-height: 23.99147605896px; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 19px; color: rgb(192, 0, 0); box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></strong></span></p>
             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">3、企业内训价6.8万（培训30名中高层，二天一夜）</span></p>
             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;" /></span></p>
             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">4、【报名电话】<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 27.9971580505371px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;">137-2539-6393</span></span> <span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;">陈老师。</span></span></p>
             <p style="color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; min-height: 1em; white-space: pre-wrap; line-height: 24px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 28px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;"> 【贵宾热线】 400-066-3903</span></p>
